    <item>
      <title>受中国数据好坏参半影响，油价在周度上涨后下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-17</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在创下 4 月初以来最大单周涨幅后下跌，因交易商衡量中国发布的一系列数据显示上个月工业扩张放缓，而零售额超过预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-17</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 23:29:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
